<li>I'll always remember [Deceased's Name]'s [positive quality/memory].</li>
<li> Your friendship meant so much to [Deceased's Name].</li>
<li>I'm here for you if you want to talk, cry, or just sit in silence.</li>
<li> Sending you a hug and all my love.</li>
<li> May peace be with you during this difficult journey.</li>
